data.description: Whoa! Check out this Ghent Beauty! Turn of the century charm & character w/2023 amenities! "The Clifford House" is adorned by welcoming gas lamps @ front entry, coded access, dedicated off-street parking + private storage (approx 12' x 12'!) in nice (dry!) basement! Surprisingly lg bdrms, living & dining spaces, 2 modern baths, lg porch/balcony w/ceiling fan. Architectural highlights include exposed brick, broad moldings & baseboards, arches,+ a beautiful period fireplace (decorative). Lovely! Main living area lighting & hallway sconces new, fresh paint throughout, too. Modern kitchen includes new granite, high-end full bowl sink that just might wash the dishes for you, bar seating @ main island. Large primary w/en-suite bath, dual sinks, private water closet. AAACK ALL THE WINDOWS! They're gorgeous! Theaters, dining, art, food, nightlife, history, EVMS, ODU-just a short distance away! Harris Teeter grocery less than 1 block! h20/sewer/trash incl'd in condo fees. EZ Access to NOB, NAS.
